# This directory stores product candidates awaiting human review.
#
# Files:
#   pending_review.json   - Products discovered by crawler, waiting for approval
#   approved_archive.json - Log of approved candidates
#   candidates_*.json     - Archived previous candidate batches
#
# Workflow:
#   1. Run: python main.py --generate-candidates
#   2. Review: python tools/list_candidates.py
#   3. Approve: python tools/approve_candidate.py "ProductName"
#
# Approved products are moved to data/products_featured.json
